data.title: Destination Small Town
data.text:
Regular Business Hours:

Monday - Friday 8:00 am-5:00 pm

The City Council meets the 2nd & 4th Monday of every month at 6:00 pm in Council Chambers at City Hall.

Visit our county page and you will find information about our town and county's points of interest, festivals/events and faith community. You also will find stories about the contributions made by farmers/ranchers located throughout our county and of course you will learn about the community organizations that have built and continue to build strong communities (chambers, community groups, and departments, etc) and much more when you visit the Dodge County, MN page.
